        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>蓝调细雨时刻。</p>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>蓝调细雨时刻。</p>
<!-- more -->
<br>
<h1 id="起意">起意</h1>
<p>这天白了一整天，闷的要死。<br>
终于憋到傍晚，淅沥下起小雨。<br>
那还说啥了，拍！</p>
<br>
<p>本期在修图时，为了符合雨天的氛围，尽可能采用了偏蓝的色调。</p>
<br>
<h1 id="花白-蕊黄-苞绿-果红">花白 蕊黄 苞绿 果红</h1>
<p>植物这一块。<br>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P1edcbc9a91e901baf.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P1" class="gallery-img"><br>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P217635bb37147a76f.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P2" class="gallery-img"><br>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P31d1f6898f35c84ed.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P3" class="gallery-img"><br>
▲白叶身淋雨滴，黄蕊轻语生命的真谛。</p>
<br>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P5be3b8aa4578b5296.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P5" class="gallery-img">
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P64a6b457497e46d84.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P6" class="gallery-img">
▲绿苞又在一旁，乘着春雨，静待春来。    
<br>
<br>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P4a814342084b23643.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P4" class="gallery-img">
▲红果散落一地，无人识，无人捡，正如雨来，又随雨去。
<p><br><br></p>
<h1 id="捕光追影">捕光追影</h1>
<p>路灯作为一种光源，在雨天自然也特别出片。<br>
后两张的炫光由于雨滴在了镜头上，虽然看似废片，但个人感觉也挺有一番风味，遂保留。<br>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P79de54c3dd8c36647.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P7" class="gallery-img"><br>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P8d2a652ceb1e274ea.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P8" class="gallery-img"><br>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P95dbab687270866c3.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P9" class="gallery-img"></p>
<p><br><br></p>
<h1 id="倚树紫花">倚树紫花</h1>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P10f565483356b57527.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P10" class="gallery-img">
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P137e88724f43a1524e.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P13" class="gallery-img">
▲于树角落，孤芳自赏
<br><br>
<h1 id="闪灯之下">闪灯之下</h1>
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P112c1c80a35daa6e27.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P11" class="gallery-img">
<img src="https://origin.picgo.net/2026/03/30/MWSP20260330_P12ac27e7a6bed40d4c.jpg" alt="MWSP20260330 P12" class="gallery-img">
▲咔嚓！咔嚓！
<br><br>
<h1 id="结尾">结尾</h1>
<p>依旧感谢你观看本期的作品集！<br>
雨天拍摄也挺有意思的哈哈哈～</p>
<br>
<p>本期共 13 幅作品。<br>
均拍摄于 2026.3.30，<br>
且均经过后期处理。<br>
本文写于 2026.3.30。<br>
<br></p>
<p>下期见辣！</p>
<br>
<p>某个老王 MogroWang</p>
]]></content>
